addObjectOfInterest

public boolean addObjectOfInterest(Transformable trans)
when objectsOfInterest is empty, all objects are of interest. when objectsOfInterest has one element, it will always be picked. when objectsOfInterest has more than one element, mouseDragged behavior will only occur if an objectOfInterest is picked only firstClass objects will be considered

removeObjectOfInterest

public boolean removeObjectOfInterest(Transformable trans)
when objectsOfInterest is empty, all objects are of interest. when objectsOfInterest has one element, it will always be picked. when objectsOfInterest has more than one element, mouseDragged behavior will only occur if an objectOfInterest is picked only firstClass objects will be considered
